You'll need to create a radarr user in order to run with the provided init
script:

  # useradd -r -d /var/lib/radarr radarr

You'll also need to add the following to /etc/rc.d/rc.local

if [ -x /etc/rc.d/rc.radarr ]; then
    /etc/rc.d/rc./radarr start
fi

And the following to /etc/rc.d/rc.local_shutdown

if [ -x /etc/rc.d/rc.radarr ]; then
    /etc/rc.d/rc./radarr stop
fi

